text: Sheikhupura District () is a district of Punjab province, Pakistan. Sheikhupura is the headquarters of Sheikhupura District. ==Administration== The district has 5 Tehsils: *Sheikhupura *Ferozewala *Muridke *Sharaqpur *Safdarabad Category:Districts of Punjab (Pakistan) Category:Lahore Division
title: Sheikhupura District
